---
title: Vietnamese Pho with Kale and Enoki Mushrooms
description: Our version of the classic Vietnamese rice noodle soup includes delicious enoki mushrooms and fibre-rich kale! Ginger and Thai basil create a fragrant slurp-worthy broth and the carrot ribbons add a splash of colour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vietnamese-pho-7d1c31cd.jpg
